*/15 * * * * /usr/local/bin/python3 /app/web-monitor.py -u https://lookingglass.pccwglobal.com/ > /proc/1/fd/1 2>/proc/1/fd/2
#
# Run the Python script every 15 minutes and
# redirect stdout and stderr to the main process with
# the PID of 1 to make them available through Docker logs
#
# Usage: web-monitor.py [-e] -u <url>
#
# Option:
#   -h
#     Display usage
#   -e, --email
#     Send email notification on changes
#   -u, --url
#     The URL of interest
